snippet.textDisplay: I have always been a fan of musicians from Pakistan, and have found so many amazing musicians brought together in the Coke Studio platform. However, this one right here has surpassed anything I had expeirenced previously from them. It fills me with enourmous joy, for the divine musical talent Rahat saab and Amjad saab showcased. At the same time it fills me with great sadness when I helplessly realize that we'll not have more of Amjad Sabri. Our future generations will never forgive us for letting this kind of things happen at our watch. Love and respect!
